Titolo: Hammer of the Gods (video game)

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Hammer of the Gods is a 1994 turn-based strategy computer game developed by Holistic Design and published by New World Computing for DOS. The events of the game take place in Viking Age Europe, with a Norse fantasy setting. Hammer of the Gods is one of the games that spawned the creation of the Heroes of Might and Magic strategy series.

Genere: Turn-based strategy

Valutazione: N/A
